        "timestamp": "2018-06-06 12:51:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nWe'll keep the checkins smaller any more. This one brings in the APEX main method, the APEX parameter handling, and the interfaces for events.\n\nThere's a lot of JSON test code in this check in, there's a full policy model and a lot of JSON property files for checking various configuraitons for APEX.\n\nHere's the cloc figures, it probably excludes comments which accounts for the difference. \ncloc services\n     156 text files.\n     156 unique files.                                          \n       1 file ignored.\n\ngithub.com/AlDanial/cloc v 1.74  T=0.76 s (205.1 files/s, 31370.6 lines/s)\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nLanguage                     files          blank        comment           code\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nJSON                            54              7              0           9572\nJava                            98           1649           5587           6697\nMaven                            2             13             33            105\nXML                              1              9             17             24\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nSUM:                           155           1678           5637          16398\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------",
